# UI/UX Refactor Task Allowlist
# 
# This file specifies which files may be edited for each task.
# Format: <task-id>: <glob-pattern>
#
# Example:
# P1-031: frontend/src/components/ui/**
# P1-031: frontend/src/pages/LoginPage.{jsx,css}
#
# To add a new task, add lines with the task ID and allowed file patterns.
#
# Blocked by default:
# - package.json, lockfiles, .env*
# - frontend/index.html (CSP changes need [CSP-CHANGE] tag)
# - worker/**/* (worker code needs [AUTH] tag)

